# Pass 0123 Ledger: Field-to-Proof Packet Factory

Date: 2026-07-01

## Objective

Turn the previous market and runtime passes into a market-facing product
architecture: a family of field-specific proof-packet factories. This pass is
not a broad capability inventory. It defines the canonical packet slots,
source-backed field templates, ranked products, demo order, and a small
coverage experiment that rejects an incomplete packet shape.

